Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: CBRE is pleased to offer for sale a total of ± 5.05 acres for multifamily residential uses located in The Meadows, a 420 acre master-planned community, nestled in the Rosewood neighborhood of Saskatoon, SK. When completed, The Meadows will feature 2,200+ new homes and 65 acres of parks, ponds and pathways. Within the Meadows, lies the Meadows Market, a retail power centre with Costco, boutiques, restaurants, and many more  amenities. Overall, the site is well situated within Saskatoon and is a short 7 minute drive to the city center.

CBRE Limited is pleased to offer for sale this 0.4 acre multifamily development site in prestigious Varsity View. Zoned RM3 this site currently consists of five (5) houses and offers the opportunity for the construction of a low-rise, ~24-28 suite, apartment/condo building. The Development has the potential to be the standout rental property in the Varsity View neighborhood. CBRE Limited is pleased to offer for sale this 0.4 acre multifamily development site in prestigious Varsity View. Zoned RM3 this site currently consists of five (5) houses and offers the opportunity for the construction of a low-rise, ~24-28 suite, apartment/condo building. The Development has the potential to be the standout rental property in the Varsity View neighborhood. The Subject Property is conveniently located just minutes from the University of Saskatchewan next at the intersection of Clarence Avenue South and Colony Street in Saskatoon’s east-side.

CBRE Limited is pleased to offer for sale a total of ±86.61 acres for residential uses that includes 46 serviced lots in the northern portion of the Kensington neighbourhood in Saskatoon. The development lands, which comprise of ±86.61 acres, are designated for a mix of low and medium density residential uses and the 46 lots range in size from 28 feet to 54 feet.
